【独家】红会等非定向捐赠医疗物资分配方案明确 3日前的一件不留。
[Exclusive] The distribution plan for non-directed donations of medical supplies, such as ICRC, is not retained until 3 days ago.
程璐洋2020-02-04 23:42。
cellulose 2020-02-04 23: 42
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网见习记者程璐洋2月4日，经济观察网从湖北省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部和湖北省卫生健康委员会获悉，湖北省红十字会、慈善总会和青少年发展基金会3家机构接收的非定向捐赠医疗防控物资分配方案明确。
Cellulose economy watch network from Hubei Province, the new coronavirus infection pneumonia command and Hubei Provincial Health and Hygiene Committee learned that the Hubei Red Cross Society, General Association of Charities and Foundation for Youth Development in Hubei Province received a clear allocation plan for non-targeted donations of medical materials for prevention and control.
。
.
湖北省防控指挥部物资保障组工作人员邓忠明对经济观察网介绍，该方案首先明确了物资范围，即湖北省红十字会、湖北省慈善总会、湖北省青少年发展基金会3家机构接收的非定向医疗防控物资，主要为医用防护类物资、消毒类用品、防御类药品和诊断类用品等与医疗有关、相对紧俏的物资。
Deng Zhongming, a material support group of the Hubei Provincial Control and Prevention Command, told the Economic Observation Network that the program first identified the material scope of nontargeted medical prevention and control materials received by three organizations, namely the Hubei Red Cross Society, Hubei Provincial Charitable Association and Hubei Provincial Youth Development Foundation.
。
.
分配流程可分为四步：。
The allocation process can be divided into four steps:
第一，接收，由湖北省红十字会、慈善总会、青少年发展基金会3家机构按照原流程，进行物资的接收、清理、存放，以及清单的整理等。
First, accept, by Hubei Red Cross Society, General Association of Charity, Youth Development Foundation 3 organizations according to the original process, material receiving, cleaning, storage, and inventory collation.
。
.
第二，3家机构把实实在在到位的，可供分配的非定向捐赠物资报到湖北省疫情防控指挥部。
Second, three agencies reported non-targeted donated materials that were actually in place for distribution to the Hubei Provincial Command for Disease Control and Prevention.
。
.
第三，湖北省疫情防控指挥部物资保障组对这些物资进行核实、确定，明确物资类型，以及确实已到仓库可用。
Third, the material support group of the Hubei Provincial Command of Disease Control verified and confirmed these materials, determined the type of materials and actually arrived at the warehouse for use.
确定物资清单后，物资保障组报领导审批，然后报给湖北省卫健委系统。
After confirming the material list, the material support group reports to the leader for approval and then to the Hubei Wei Bodybuilding Commission system.
。
.
第四，卫健委掌握着医院需求，确定分配去向以后，把分配方案返给物资保障组，由物资保障组把分配方案给到3家机构，3家机构对应各自上报的物资进行分配。
Fourth, the health-care committee grasped the needs of the hospital, determined the allocation, returned the distribution plan to the material security group, which assigned the distribution programme to three agencies, and three agencies allocated their respective reported materials.
。
.
湖北省邮政公司负责具体配送，送至医院后，会把签收单汇总交给红会等3家机构，再由3家机构汇总交回给物资保障组。
Hubei Post Company is responsible for the specific distribution, after the delivery to the hospital, will sign the receipt of a summary to the Red Cross and other 3 institutions, and then the three agencies aggregate back to the material security group.
。
.
至此，饱受争议的湖北救援物资分配终于有了明确的流程规范。
So far, the controversial distribution of relief materials in Hubei Province finally has a clear flow of norms.
。
.
再具体到卫健委的分配环节，物资保障组工作人员伍文洲向经济观察网介绍，湖北省卫健委有一个6人组成的团队，每天早上10点整理出各市州前一天上报的住院人数，根据这份住院人数清单结合各市州医疗工作者数量，省卫建委根据人数计算出各项物资的需求总量，得出各市州对应的物资分配系数，再根据省指挥部物资保障组报来的捐赠物资，得出各市州应分配的医用物资数量。
Wu Wenzhou, a staff member of the material support group, told the Economic Observation Network that a six-member team worked out the number of hospitalizations reported the previous day in each city state.
。
.
“举个例子，比如说现在全省需求是100万个口罩，某一个市需求1万，那么他就占我的总量的1%。
"For example, now the province needs a million masks and a city needs 10,000, and he accounts for 1 percent of my total," he said.
我这时候得到了1万个可以分配的物资，那么1万乘以1%，那就给他分100个。
I had ten thousand things to distribute by this time, and ten thousand multiplied by one percent, I gave him a hundred.
”伍文洲说，所有物资都是按符合需求的比例，保证大家都能够按照任务量和需求来分配，避免有的分多有的少了，有的资源不够，有的资源浪费。
Wu said all supplies were distributed in proportion to demand, ensuring that everyone was able to distribute according to their workload and needs, avoiding excessive, under-resourced or wasted resources.
。
.
“从省指挥部把慈善机构的物资清单给我，到我最后把分配建议提出来给他，只有一个小时。
"Give me the list of charities from the Provincial Command until I finally give him the assignment proposal, only an hour.
”伍文洲强调。
Wu Wenzhou stressed.
。
.
经济观察网了解到，3日上午，湖北指挥部物资保障组、卫健委、3家机构以及湖北省邮政公司召开了协调会，沟通了上述机制的具体细节。
The Economic Observation Network understands that on the morning of March 3, the Hubei Command Material Guarantee Team, the Wei Bodyguard Commission, three agencies and Hubei Postal Corporation held a coordination meeting and communicated the details of the above-mentioned mechanism.
。
.
截至3日，3家机构接收的非定向捐赠物资，一次性全部分发了下去，“不留，一件都不留，这是昨天的工作。
As of March 3, three institutions received non-targeted donations, a one-time distribution of all, "no stay, not a single one, this is yesterday's work.
”邓忠明说。
"said Teng.
。
.
4日开始，分配方案有了进一步优化以提高速度，“即到、即报、即批、即配”，邓忠明介绍，物资到了武汉，即刻上报、审核批准、配送，不再留存。
Since then, the distribution plan has been further optimized to improve the speed, that is to say, to report, that is, to approve, to match, "Deng Zhongming said, materials to Wuhan, immediately reported, review and approval, distribution, no longer retained.
。
.
截至4日下午6点，今天到达的2批物资已经分配完毕。
As of 6 p.m. on the fourth day, two consignments that arrived today had been distributed.
。
.
需要注意的是，上述方案针对3家机构接收的非定向医疗物资，定向捐赠物资仍由3家机构协调物流公司配送。
It should be noted that the above-mentioned programme targets non-targeted medical supplies received by three institutions, while the distribution of targeted donations is still coordinated by three agencies.
。
.
邓忠明介绍，只要有捐赠物资，每天早上8点钟，都会在湖北省政府网站上做公示，3日配送的物资，目前已有公示。
Deng Zhongming said that as long as there are donated materials, every morning at 8 o'clock, Hubei provincial government website to do public notice, 3 days of the distribution of materials, has been published.
。
.
湖北省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部物资保障组医用防护物资调度情况公示。
The new coronavirus infection pneumonia epidemic prevention and control command material support group medical protection material dispatching public.
为什么上述物资调度情况公示中，社会非定向捐赠的第一批物资还根据捐赠人意愿分配至相关市州？。
Why is it that the first batch of non-targeted donations is distributed to the relevant city states according to the donor's wishes?
伍文洲解释，在物资分配下去前，非定向捐赠人都可以向捐赠机构要求修改捐赠地区。
Wu explained that non-targeted donors could request donor agencies to modify the donor area before distributing goods.
有些数量较少的非定向物资，省卫健委则按照向重点疫区倾斜的原则，分配给武汉市、黄冈市等地区。
Some quantity of non-targeted materials, the provincial health care committee in accordance with the principle of tilting to key epidemic areas, such as Wuhan, Huanggang City and other areas.
“如果数量不多还平均分配，有的地方只分一点点，还要四五百公里送过去。
"If they are not distributed equally, there are places only a little bit, and four or five hundred kilometres to go.
”。
"
与物资分配方案明确同步的是，对物资统筹不力的情况，相应的处罚结果也相继曝出。
In tandem with the material distribution programme, the lack of integration of material resources has been accompanied by the corresponding penalties.
。
.
2月4日，据湖北省纪委监委网站，湖北省红十字会3名领导被处分。
On February 4, three leaders of the Hubei Red Cross Society were disciplined, according to the Hubei Provincial Disciplinary Committee's website.
。
.
湖北省纪委监委通报，湖北省红十字会有关领导和干部在疫情防控期间接收和分配捐赠款物工作中存在不担当不作为、违反“三重一大”规定、信息公开错误等失职失责问题。
Hubei Provincial Disciplinary Committee informed that the leaders and cadres of the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province had failed to take the responsibility of inaction, violating the "triple big" regulation and information disclosure error in receiving and distributing donations during the period of epidemic prevention and control.
经省纪委监委研究并报省委批准，对专职副会长张钦、党组成员陈波、党组书记兼常务副会长高勤等分别给予免职、记大过、严重警告等处分。
After being studied by the provincial disciplinary committee and submitted to the provincial committee for approval, full-time vice-chairman Zhang Qin, Party member Chen Bo, party secretary and permanent vice-president Gao Qin were given dismissal, serious warning and other sanctions respectively.
省红十字会其他责任人员由有关党组织依纪依规处理。
Other responsible personnel of the provincial Red Cross Society shall be handled according to discipline by relevant Party organizations.
。
.
同时，据湖北日报，武汉市严肃查处了市防疫应急物资储备仓库违规发放口罩问题，纪委监委问责3名职能部门领导。
Meanwhile, according to the Hubei Daily, Wuhan seriously investigated and dealt with the issue of illegal issue of masks from the city's emergency supplies warehouse.
。
.
